A low-pressure air event happen.
More dust in the air will be
push down to the ground.

in your tablet. You should check it out.

Today, It's a lovely day.
Good weather, fresh air, lively neighbor.
No dust bother you.

No matter how hard you tried to live, by yourself,
you'll die anyway. You need to fix at the root cause,
the origin of the dust. Not just use mask,
it just helps you stay longer, only you.

So come with us, We can change this together with Greenpeace.
